Intelligent Addressable Fire Alarm System NFS2-640

The NFS2-640 intelligent Fire Alarm Control Panel is part of the ONYX® Series of Fire Alarm Controls from NOTIFIER.

<>

Smoke Detectors with Sounder and Relay Option

System Sensor i3™ sounder and relay smoke detectors apply the guiding principles of installation ease, intelligence, and instant inspection in a series of specialty conventional devices.

<>

Smoke & Heat Detector Remote LED 2151T

The 2151 low-profile photoelectronic detector uses a state-of-the-art optical sensing chamber. This detector is designed to provide open area protection and to be used with compatible UL listed control panels only.

<>

Horn-Strobe Light Red SYS-HSS

ystem Sensor selectable output horns, strobes, and horn strobes are rich with features guaranteed to reduce installation times and maximize profits.

<>

Selectable Output Low Frequency Sounder SPRL

The SpectrAlert Advance series offers the most versatile and easy-to-use line of low frequency sounder and low frequency sounder strobes in the industry.

<>

Indoor Selectable Output Speaker Strobes SPSRL

System Sensor L-Series selectable output speaker strobes and dual-voltage evacuation speakers can reduce ground faults and enable faster installation with lower current draw and modern aesthetics.

<>

Intelligent Addressable Fire Alarm System NFS-320

The NFS-320 intelligent Fire Alarm Control Panel is part of the ONYX® Series of Fire Alarm Controls from NOTIFIER.

<>

Alarm Bells SSM Series

System Sensor’s SSM Series alarm bells are low-current, high-decibel notification appliances for use in fire and burglary systems or other signaling applications.

<>

Addressable Fire Alarm System NFS2-3030

The NFS2-3030 is an intelligent Fire Alarm Control Panel designed for medium- to large-scale facilities.

<>

Low-Profile Plug-in Smoke/Heat Detector 800 Series

System Sensor’s 800 series detectors are 2-wire conventional profile plug-in detectors aimed to meet the performance criteria designated by UL.

<>
